title: Ginkgo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Changing lunch menu with labelled vegan items. Dinner menu always has two labelled vegan and two labelled ovo-lacto main courses, and a vegan dessert (e.g. apple crumble with almond rosemary ice cream). Also vegan cake in the afternoon, coffee optional with soy milk. Vegan breakfast.  Has gluten free options.
